name: #14 Ketamine
description: Ketamine is used by medical practitioners and veterinarians as an aesthetic, sometimes used illegally by people to get high. It is a dissociative drug, which means it acts on different chemicals in the brain to produce visual and auditory distortion and a detachment from reality. When it is sold illegally, ketamine usually comes as a white or off-white powder, even pills or dissolved in a liquid.
